      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i need help with a trip to tokyo next week. im going to be mostly in the shibuya and marunouchi areas for meetings. can u help me put together a basic itinerary for a monday to friday? i mostly just need to know how much time to budget for travel between those two districts and if u know any quiet cafes nearby that are actually good for working. thanks.",
